quran[1]{c,v,t}:
  73,20,"Ih, Iรฉรดa Mass ik, keรงรง akked urbaรข seg wid illan yidek, teppekkrem deg iv, qรดib sin imuren, ne$ azgen, ne$ amur wis kuรฉ. ร–ebbi Iwezzen iv akked wass; Iรฉรดa ur ten tรชepbem ara. Issuref awen. E$รดet, si Leqwรดan, ayen isehlen fellawen. Iรฉรดa ad ilin segwen imuvan. Wiyav ppinigen di tmurt, pnadin lfevl n ร–ebbi. Wiyav pna$en deg ubrid n ร–ebbi. Ihi, e$รดet, segs, ayen isehlen fellawen; รฉallet; zekkit; รดevlet aS i ร–ebbi, aรดeรฎรฎal umรขin. Lxiรด ara txedmem i iman nnwen, a t tafem ar ร–ebbi. D arraz it yifen, it i$elben. Ssutret ssmaรช i ร–ebbi. Ih, ร–ebbi Ipsemmiรช, Ipรชunu"